CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, November 15, 1938, pg. unknown, reads: "William A. Harris, Jr., son of the well known sportsman of Pittsburgh, Pa., 'Woogie' Harris.  Young master Harris seems to be definitely heading towards the popularity his dad now enjoys."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of William Harris, son of William "Woogie" Harris, posed in Loendi Club
